Biscotti

2 c ap flour
1 c granulated sugar
1 c pistachio nuts
1/4 tsp baking powder
2 eggs
1 egg yolk
lemon zest from 1 lemon
orange zest from 1 orange

Preheat oven to 350F. Add the flour, sugar, baking powder, and zests in the bowl of a stand mixer fitted with a paddle attachment. Mix until combined. With the machine running, add the eggs and the nuts, then form into a dough. Roll on a floured surface into a sausage shape. Place the dough on a baking sheet and bake for 20 min. Slice into rounds and return to the oven until crisp.

Variations:

Lime & Chive
change the pistachio and zests for 2 tsp of snipped chives and zest of 3 limes.

Chocolate & Orange:
omit the pistachio and add 3/4 c cocoa powder and 1/2 c chopped chocolate pieces

Lemon & Ginger:
Omit pistachio nuts & orange zest. Add 1 tsp of ground ginger.
